The paper discusses a novel approach for distributed performance monitoring of soft-real time distributed systems, which involves employing distributed algorithms from statistical signal processing and learning domains. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
